### 3. Cambiar rol a Professional (requiere token)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/change-role
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "roleName": "Professional"
}

###

### 4. Cambiar rol a Admin (requiere token)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/change-role
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "roleName": "Admin"
}

